                                </small></div><div class="cleardescription">Pełen profesjonalizm ! Expresowa wysyłka. Będę tu kupował :-)</div></div><div class="product_wrapper col-md-3 col-xs-6 type_opinion" id="hot4_8"><a class="product-icon" data-product-id="" href="/product-pol-5707-Nikka-From-The-Barrel-51-4-0-5l.html" title="Nikka From The Barrel / 51,4% / 0,5l"><img src="/gfx/pol/loader.gif?r=1518081870" class="b-lazy" data-src-small="/pol_is_Nikka-From-The-Barrel-51-4-0-5l-5707.jpg" data-src="/pol_il_Nikka-From-The-Barrel-51-4-0-5l-5707.jpg" alt="Nikka From The Barrel / 51,4% / 0,5l"></a><div class="producer"></div><a class="product-name" href="/product-pol-5707-Nikka-From-The-Barrel-51-4-0-5l.html" title="Nikka From The Barrel / 51,4% / 0,5l">Nikka From The Barrel / 51,4% / 0,5l</a><div class="traits"></div><div class="gold-separator"></div><div class="product_prices"><span class="price">157,00 zł</span></div><div class="client">Kamil, Szczecin</div><div class="note"><span><i class="icon-star active"></i><i class="icon-star active"></i><i class="icon-star active"></i><i class="icon-star active"></i><i class="icon-star"></i></span><small>
